&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:24px; margin-bottom:8px&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Submission Guidelines&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:8px; margin-bottom:8px; text-align:justify; text-indent:18.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;Please send your extended abstracts to Dr. Wang via email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:2025climateleadership@gmail.com&quot;&gt;2025climateleadership@gmail.com&lt;/a&gt;. Submissions should include:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

