&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:24px; margin-bottom:8px&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Registration Fees&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:8px; margin-bottom:8px; text-align:justify; text-indent:36.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-justify:inter-ideograph&quot;&gt;There is NO registration fee for the conference. Lunches will be provided during the conference period. Participants are responsible for their own travel, accommodation, and other personal expenses.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

